Gil Birmingham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gil_Birmingham 0 Gil Birmingham (born July 13, 1953) is an American actor of Comanche ancestry, best known for his portrayal of Billy Black in The Twilight Saga film series and his recurring role as Virgil White in Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt.
